file.name: OpenApi_defn_multipart.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
paths:
  /v3/openapi/multipartObject:
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          multipart/form-data:
            schema:
              properties:
                person:
                  type: object
                  properties:
                    name:
                      type: string
                    age:
                      type: number
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
  /v3/openapi/multipartBinary:
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          multipart/form-data:
            schema:
              properties:
                file:
                  type: string
                  format: binary
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
  /v3/openapi/multipartArray:
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          multipart/form-data:
            schema:
              properties:
                people:
                  type: array
                  items:
                    type: object
                    properties:
                      name:
                        type: string
                      age:
                        type: number
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
  /v3/openapi/multipartOther:
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          multipart/form-data:
            schema:
              properties:
                organization:
                  type: string
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
  /v3/openapi/multipartMultiple:
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          multipart/form-data:
            schema:
              properties:
                additionalMetadata:
                  type: string
                  description: Additional data to pass to server
                file:
                  type: string
                  description: file to upload
                  format: binary
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
